Watch: Demonstrators in the streets of Mexico City burn Trump pi単atas Posted at 4:49 pm on February 12, 2017 by Jacob B. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
Anti-Trump demonstrations are taking place today in the streets of cities across Mexico. Here are some of the images and videos of the activity. Massive Anti-Trump rallies in #Mexico today. 18 cities total. The slogan: 'Mexico deserves respect'. Don't miss our coverage @MSNBC #VibraMx pic.twitter.com/ZNSN4xkwnG
